Your problem is exactly the reason why you should not use this method of inserting data. &lt;br/&gt; The recommended way is the method [`insert()`][1] like this:

    ContentValues cv = new ContentValues(); 
    cv.put(&quot;Title&quot;, thisTitle);
    cv.put(&quot;Artist&quot;, thisArtist);
    cv.put(&quot;Numb&quot;, &quot;1&quot;);
    db.insert(&quot;DBExample&quot;, null, cv);
By using a `ContentValues` object you don&#39;t have to worry about the data type of the values and escaping special characters like single quotes.&lt;br/&gt;
But if you insist on using your method, you must know that you take the risk of [sql injection][2]. &lt;br/&gt;


